<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/13199.Alain_de_Botton"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1189753902p3/13199.jpg);'></div>
